'''基思·諾爾·埃默森'''（{{lang-en|Keith Noel Emerson}}，{{bd|1944年|11月2日|2016年|3月11日}}），是[[英國|英國]]的[[鍵盤手|鍵盤手]]，{{link-en|約克郡西瑞丁|West Riding of Yorkshire}}[[托德摩登|托德摩登]]人。在他的音樂生涯中，他加入過 Keith Emerson Trio、John Brown's Bodies、Gary Farr and the T-Bones、 the V.I.P.s同P. P. Arnold's backing band the Nice樂隊。

2016年3月11日，埃默森在[[美國|美國]][[加州|加州]][[聖莫尼卡_(加利福尼亞州)|聖莫尼卡]]開槍自殺，終年71歲<ref name="nytobit">{{cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/03/12/arts/music/keith-emerson-70s-rock-showman-with-a-taste-for-spectacle-dies-at-71.html?_r=0 |title=Keith Emerson, ’70s Rock Showman With a Taste for Spectacle, Dies at 71 |first=Ben |last=Ratliff |newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |page=B7 |date=11 March 2016 |accessdate=2016-03-21 |archive-date=2017-08-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170827130853/https://www.nytimes.com/2016/03/12/arts/music/keith-emerson-70s-rock-showman-with-a-taste-for-spectacle-dies-at-71.html?_r=0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。當地警方在事發後第二天，在埃默森的住所找到他的屍體<ref name="krebs">Daniel Kreps, "Keith Emerson, Emerson, Lake and Palmer Keyboardist, Dead at 71," ''[[Rolling_Stone|Rolling Stone]]'' New York, accessed on 11 March 2016. [http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/keith-emerson-emerson-lake-and-palmer-keyboardist-dead-at-71-20160311] {{Wayback|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/keith-emerson-emerson-lake-and-palmer-keyboardist-dead-at-71-20160311 |date=20160312093601 }}</ref>。

